          quote: 'Dear Magwitch, I must tell you, now at last. You had a child once, whom you loved and lost... She is a lady and very beautiful. And I love her!',
          analysis: 'Pip\'s finest moment — offering comfort to a dying man by connecting the threads of love that have bound them all. Compassion transcends class.',
